description: Dog ownership is a privilege. It takes time and effort that we sometimes aren't ready for. The biggest obstacle people face when becoming a dog owner is building a healthy and respectful relationship with their dog. This relationship translates into all areas of dog training. Not only will the Dog Obedience ebook teach you the formula for training your dog, it is also a guide for you to understand why your pet acts the way it does - good or bad. Learn about signals for your puppy or canine that will teach them to obey their owner. Take the stress out of dog training and take command with the Dog Obedience book.
